sub_title: Mastering unbiased thinking | Mindful career coach & researcher | Life, mental health & work must be friends | Sharing my insights & perspective along the way
summary:
As a certified career coach and psychology researcher, I'm passionate about tailoring experiences, models, and systems to help my clients unlock their full potential. With a deep understanding of the unique challenges that individuals from diverse backgrounds may face, I'm committed to guiding my clients with resilience and confidence.

Having overcome significant challenges related to career change, immigration, and mental health myself, I'm dedicated to helping others navigate obstacles and uncover their talents, passions, and interests. I believe in the power of unbiased thinking and helping people shed harmful beliefs that can hold them back from achieving their goals.

I am always open to creating new connections and sharing knowledge and experience. So, if you're looking for a trusted partner in your personal or professional journey, feel free to reach out, and let's see how we make life experiences more unbiased, meaningful, and fulfilling.
